OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChancellor must do more to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhelp poorest households,   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcharity says               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A leading debt charity is calling on   
OL,6, the chancellor to use this week's      
OL,7, Spring Statement to do more to help    
OL,8, poorer households.                     
OL,10,FStepChange is calling on Rishi Sunak to
OL,11,Fincrease welfare benefits and offer    
OL,12,Fmore help with energy bills.           
OL,14,FWithout that, many more people will    
OL,15,Ffall into "problem debt" the charity   
OL,16,Fsaid.                                  
OL,18,FMr Sunak told the BBC he cannot "fully 
OL,19,Fprotect" people from the consequences  
OL,20,Fof rising prices.                      
